<div class="l-page-shell l-module-stack about-page">
  <section class="card card-impact about-hero" aria-labelledby="about-hero-heading">
    <div class="l-grid--2 about-hero__intro">
      <div class="l-module-stack">
        <p class="about-kicker">01 / Hero</p>
        <h1 class="card-title display-title" id="about-hero-heading">Who Musifer Is</h1>
        <p>
          Musifer is being built as an artist-first home base for practical guidance, clear next steps,
          and long-term support. The goal is simple: reduce confusion for independent artists and make progress feel possible.
        </p>
      </div>
      <aside class="about-hero__visual" aria-label="Brand motif preview">
        <img class="content-logo" src="/Images/Musifer_Logo.svg" alt="Musifer brand mark">
        <p>Independent by default. Built in public. Evolving with artists.</p>
      </aside>
    </div>
    <div class="l-grid--3 about-callouts" aria-label="Quick value points">
      <article class="about-panel">
        <h2 class="card-title">Artist-first support</h2>
        <p>Practical resources designed for early-career and independent creators.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="about-panel">
        <h2 class="card-title">Actionable guidance</h2>
        <p>Clear, low-friction steps that help move projects forward.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="about-panel">
        <h2 class="card-title">Long-view platform</h2>
        <p>Current tools now, with legal and strategic layers expanding over time.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="l-grid--2 about-story-pillars" aria-label="Brand story and guiding pillars">
    <article class="card">
      <p class="about-kicker">02 / Brand Story</p>
      <h2 class="card-title">Why this exists</h2>
      <div class="l-module-stack">
        <p class="about-panel">
          Musifer started from a recurring problem: independent artists often have talent and momentum,
          but not always a reliable map for decisions around growth, workflow, and protection.
        </p>
        <p class="about-panel">
          The current phase focuses on practical resources and clearer pathways. The long-term plan is
          to expand into stronger legal and strategic support as the platform matures.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <p class="about-kicker">03 / Guiding Pillars</p>
      <h2 class="card-title">Core values</h2>
      <ul class="about-pillars-list">
        <li class="about-panel">Independent by default</li>
        <li class="about-panel">Artist-first support</li>
        <li class="about-panel">Practical resources over hype</li>
        <li class="about-panel">Future-facing platform design</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>

